[08/01/2019 04:05:02] <font color="#ffffff">(R E)</font>
[08/01/2019 04:05:06] <font color="#ffffff">-Hasta luego. Agur.</font>
[08/01/2019 04:05:06] <font color="#ffffff">-Agur.</font>
[08/01/2019 04:05:07] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola.</font>
[08/01/2019 04:05:07] <font color="#ffffff">-Hola, ¿Qué tal?</font>
