[08/01/2019 10:33:56] <font color="#ffffff">"Mapudungupe Ta Che",</font>
[08/01/2019 10:34:00] <font color="#ffffff">que es un manual</font>
[08/01/2019 10:34:00] <font color="#ffffff">con 15 actividades didácticas,</font>
