[08/01/2019 10:49:40] <font color="#ffffff">practicarlo, crecer, experimentar.</font>
[08/01/2019 10:49:59] <font color="#ffffff">¡Acción!</font>
[08/01/2019 10:50:10] <font color="#ffffff">"Cine sin Autor" primero</font>
